---
// 月供计算器 · Bespoke homepage content
---
<!-- ===== HERO + CALCULATOR ===== -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge" role="text">
      <span class="hero-badge-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      专业房贷 &amp; 车贷试算工具
    </div>
    <h1>每月<em>供几多</em>，<br>秒算即知道</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      输入贷款金额、年利率和年限，选择还款方式，<br>即时显示月供明细与完整还款计划
    </p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span>即时计算</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</span>可视化图解</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-icon" aria-hidden="true">📋</span>完整还款表</span>
      <span class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-icon" aria-hidden="true">📱</span>移动端友好</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CALCULATOR CARD -->
  <div class="calc-wrapper" id="calculator" aria-label="月供计算器">
    <div class="calc-card">
      <div class="calc-header">
        <div class="calc-header-left">
          <div class="calc-header-icon" aria-hidden="true">🧮</div>
          <div>
            <h2>月供计算器</h2>
            <p>房贷 / 车贷 / 消费贷均适用</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="loan-type-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="还款方式">
          <button class="loan-tab active" id="tab-equal-payment" role="tab" aria-selected="true" onclick="switchTab('equal-payment')">等额本息</button>
          <button class="loan-tab" id="tab-equal-principal" role="tab" aria-selected="false" onclick="switchTab('equal-principal')">等额本金</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-body">
        <!-- INPUTS -->
        <div class="calc-inputs">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label class="field-label" for="loan-amount">
              贷款总额
              <span class="field-unit">元（人民币 / AUD）</span>
            </label>
            <div class="field-input-wrap">
              <span class="field-prefix" aria-hidden="true">¥</span>
              <input class="field-input" id="loan-amount" type="number"
                     value="1000000" min="1" step="10000"
                     placeholder="如：1000000"
                     aria-label="贷款总额（元）"
                     oninput="calculate()">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field-group">
            <label class="field-label" for="annual-rate">
              年利率
              <span class="field-unit">% / 年</span>
            </label>
            <div class="field-input-wrap">
              <span class="field-prefix" aria-hidden="true">%</span>
              <input class="field-input" id="annual-rate" type="number"
                     value="4.2" min="0.01" max="30" step="0.01"
                     placeholder="如：4.20"
                     aria-label="年利率（百分比）"
                     oninput="calculate()">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field-group">
            <label class="field-label" for="loan-years">
              贷款年限
              <span class="field-unit">年</span>
            </label>
            <div class="field-input-wrap">
              <span class="field-prefix" aria-hidden="true">年</span>
              <input class="field-input" id="loan-years" type="number"
                     value="30" min="1" max="50" step="1"
                     placeholder="如：30"
                     aria-label="贷款年限（年）"
                     style="padding-left: 42px"
                     oninput="calculate()">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field-group">
            <div class="field-label">还款方式</div>
            <div class="method-group" role="radiogroup" aria-label="还款方式选择">
              <label class="method-option">
                <input type="radio" name="method" value="equal-payment" checked
                       onchange="switchTab('equal-payment')">
                <div class="method-label">
                  <span class="method-emoji">📊</span>
                  <span class="method-name">等额本息</span>
                  <span class="method-desc">每月固定，利多息少</span>
                </div>
              </label>
              <label class="method-option">
                <input type="radio" name="method" value="equal-principal"
                       onchange="switchTab('equal-principal')">
                <div class="method-label">
                  <span class="method-emoji">📉</span>
                  <span class="method-name">等额本金</span>
                  <span class="method-desc">递减还款，总息少</span>
                </div>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button class="calc-btn" onclick="calculate()" aria-label="计算月供">
            立即计算月供 ⚡
          </button>
          <p class="calc-disclaimer">
            ⚠ 以上结果仅供参考，以银行实际核定利率及合同条款为准，建议咨询专业贷款顾问。
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- RESULTS -->
        <div class="calc-results" id="calc-results" aria-live="polite">
          <div class="result-placeholder" id="result-placeholder">
            <div class="result-placeholder-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏠</div>
            <div class="result-placeholder-text">输入参数后点击「立即计算」</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Amortization -->
      <div id="amort-section" style="padding: 0 32px 24px; display:none;">
        <div class="amort-toggle" id="amort-toggle" onclick="toggleAmort()" role="button" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')toggleAmort()">
          <span class="amort-toggle-text" id="amort-toggle-text">📋 展开完整还款计划表</span>
          <span class="amort-chevron" id="amort-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amort-container" id="amort-container" role="region" aria-label="还款计划表">
          <!-- Populated by JS -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== STATS RIBBON ===== -->
<div class="stats-ribbon" aria-label="关键数据">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stats-item reveal">
        <div class="stats-num">30<span>年</span></div>
        <div class="stats-label">最长还款年限</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="stats-num">5.8<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="stats-label">澳洲现行参考利率</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="stats-num">3.45<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="stats-label">国内 5 年 LPR 参考</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="stats-num">20<span>%+</span></div>
        <div class="stats-label">典型首付比例</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<p style="text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-light);padding:8px 0;background:var(--accent-dark);">
  数据仅供参考，以银行官网为准 · 更新于 2026 年
</p>

<!-- ===== METHOD COMPARISON ===== -->
<section class="method-comparison" id="methods">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">还款方式对比</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">等额本息 vs<br>等额本金</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">两种主流还款方式各有优劣，选择前先了解核心差异</p>

    <div class="method-comparison-grid">
      <div class="method-card reveal">
        <div class="method-card-header">
          <div class="method-card-icon primary" aria-hidden="true">📊</div>
          <div>
            <div class="method-card-title">等额本息</div>
            <span class="method-card-tag tag-primary">月供恒定</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="method-card-body">
          <p class="method-card-desc">
            每月还款金额固定不变，利息占比前高后低。现金流可预测，适合收入稳定的工薪阶层。
          </p>
          <ul class="method-points">
            <li><span class="point-icon">✅</span> 每月还款额固定，便于规划家庭支出</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">✅</span> 还款压力均匀，前期负担不沉重</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">⚠️</span> 总利息支出高于等额本金</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">⚠️</span> 前期本金偿还比例低，提前还款收益相对小</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">💡</span> 适合：收入稳定、规划能力强的购房者</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="method-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="method-card-header">
          <div class="method-card-icon accent" aria-hidden="true">📉</div>
          <div>
            <div class="method-card-title">等额本金</div>
            <span class="method-card-tag tag-accent">总息最少</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="method-card-body">
          <p class="method-card-desc">
            每月偿还本金相同，利息随剩余本金减少而逐月递降。总利息支出比等额本息少。
          </p>
          <ul class="method-points">
            <li><span class="point-icon">✅</span> 总利息更少，长期成本更低</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">✅</span> 月供逐月递减，后期还款压力小</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">⚠️</span> 前期月供金额较高，初期压力大</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">⚠️</span> 首月月供可能是等额本息的 1.5–2 倍</li>
            <li><span class="point-icon">💡</span> 适合：有一定储蓄、收入较高或即将提升的人群</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PREPAYMENT TIPS ===== -->
<section id="tips">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">省息攻略</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">提前还款，省息有门道</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">合理安排还款节奏，可节省数万至数十万利息支出</p>

    <div class="tips-grid">
      <div class="tip-card reveal">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">⏰</div>
        <h3 class="tip-title">越早还越省</h3>
        <p class="tip-text">
          贷款前 1/3 期间是利息集中支出阶段。如果有额外资金，优先在前 3–5 年内提前还款，节省的利息往往是后期的 3 倍以上。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">📆</div>
        <h3 class="tip-title">每年多还一次月供</h3>
        <p class="tip-text">
          将年终奖或年度储蓄额外还一期本金，30 年贷款可缩短约 4–6 年还款期，节省利息可观。计算建议用本工具验证。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔄</div>
        <h3 class="tip-title">再融资降低利率</h3>
        <p class="tip-text">
          利率环境改变时，考虑向银行申请重新定价（重新定价 / refinance）。澳洲市场利率下行阶段，refinance 可每年省息数千至数万澳元。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏦</div>
        <h3 class="tip-title">offset 账户对冲</h3>
        <p class="tip-text">
          澳洲银行普遍提供 100% offset 账户——账户余额抵扣贷款本金计息。日常工资收入停在 offset 账户，无需提前还款也能大幅减少利息。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">💳</div>
        <h3 class="tip-title">提高还款频率</h3>
        <p class="tip-text">
          将月供改为双周或每周还款（部分银行支持），每年多还约 1 次月供的金额，相当于额外还款，有效缩短还款期限。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</div>
        <h3 class="tip-title">对比固定 vs 浮动利率</h3>
        <p class="tip-text">
          加息周期选浮动可能较省；降息周期锁定固定利率规避风险。建议结合本工具对比两种方案的总利息差异后再做决策。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== INTEREST RATE REFERENCE ===== -->
<section class="rate-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);">参考利率</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" style="color: #FFF;">主流贷款参考利率</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);">仅供参考，以各银行官网及贷款合同为准</p>

    <div class="rate-table-wrap reveal">
      <div class="rate-row header" role="row">
        <span role="columnheader">贷款类型</span>
        <span role="columnheader">参考利率</span>
        <span role="columnheader" class="bank">市场区间</span>
        <span role="columnheader">说明</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-row" role="row">
        <span class="type">🇨🇳 国内房贷（LPR）</span>
        <span class="rate-val highlight">3.45%</span>
        <span class="rate-val bank">3.10%–3.75%</span>
        <span class="rate-val">5 年期 LPR（2026 年参考）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-row" role="row">
        <span class="type">🇦🇺 澳洲浮动房贷</span>
        <span class="rate-val highlight">5.8%–6.2%</span>
        <span class="rate-val bank">5.5%–7.0%</span>
        <span class="rate-val">主要银行浮动利率参考区间</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-row" role="row">
        <span class="type">🇦🇺 澳洲固定房贷</span>
        <span class="rate-val highlight">5.5%–6.0%</span>
        <span class="rate-val bank">5.0%–6.8%</span>
        <span class="rate-val">1–5 年固定期，各行差异较大</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-row" role="row">
        <span class="type">🚗 车贷（澳洲）</span>
        <span class="rate-val highlight">6.5%–9.9%</span>
        <span class="rate-val bank">5.9%–12%</span>
        <span class="rate-val">新车优于旧车，信用评分影响大</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-row" role="row">
        <span class="type">🏢 商业贷款（澳洲）</span>
        <span class="rate-val highlight">7.0%–9.5%</span>
        <span class="rate-val bank">6.5%–11%</span>
        <span class="rate-val">视经营年限、资产及行业而定</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="rate-disclaimer reveal">⚠ 以上利率仅供参考，实际利率因借款人资质、银行政策、市场环境而异，以贷款合同为准。建议联系专业顾问获取个性化报价。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
<section id="faq" style="background: var(--bg-warm);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">常见问题</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">贷款人常问的问题</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">帮你厘清月供计算背后的逻辑</p>

    <div class="faq-list reveal" role="list">
      <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          等额本息和等额本金，哪个总利息更少？
          <span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">
            等额本金的总利息支出更少。因为等额本金方式每月偿还相同金额的本金，剩余本金递减更快，利息基数随之减少。同等条件下，等额本金节省的总利息可达等额本息的 15%–25%。但等额本金前期月供更高，需要更强的初期还款能力。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          月供计算公式是什么？
          <span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">
            <strong>等额本息</strong>：月供 = 贷款总额 × 月利率 × (1+月利率)^还款月数 ÷ [(1+月利率)^还款月数 - 1]<br><br>
            <strong>等额本金</strong>：每月还款 = 每月本金 + 当月利息 = 贷款总额÷总月数 + 剩余本金×月利率<br><br>
            其中月利率 = 年利率 ÷ 12。本工具使用上述标准公式计算，结果与各大银行计算器吻合，仅供参考。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          提前还款是否划算，怎么计算节省多少利息？
          <span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">
            提前还款是否划算，取决于「剩余贷款利率」vs「资金投资回报率」对比。若贷款利率 6%，手头资金能稳定获得 7%+ 收益，则未必立刻提前还款。若贷款利率 4–5%，且没有更高回报渠道，提前还款是最「无风险」的理财。您可用本工具对比原始总利息与提前还款后的差额。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          利率变化对月供影响有多大？
          <span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">
            以 100 万元 / 30 年等额本息贷款为例：利率从 4% 升至 5%，月供约增加 ¥600；升至 6%，月供约增加 ¥1,200。您可以在本工具中直接修改利率参数即时看到差异，无需手动对比。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          计算器支持澳洲房贷吗？
          <span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">
            完全支持。贷款额填入 AUD 金额，年利率填入澳洲银行报价（如 5.8%），年限选 25 或 30 年即可。注意澳洲银行月供计算方式与本工具标准公式一致，差异极小。如需更精确的个性化方案，建议联系专业贷款经纪人（Mortgage Broker）咨询。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
<section class="cta-section" id="consult">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <p class="section-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); margin-bottom: 8px;">专业贷款顾问</p>
      <h2 class="cta-title reveal">算完了，下一步让专家帮你落地</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub reveal">Arrivau 贷款团队提供澳洲房贷、商业贷款、refinance 全流程服务，免费评估，不成功不收费</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons reveal">
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary" aria-label="免费咨询 Arrivau 贷款顾问">免费咨询贷款顾问 →</a>
        <a href="#calculator" class="btn-ghost">重新试算</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== EDITORIAL PICKS ===== -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">编辑精选</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">贷款知识精选</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">由专业编辑团队整理，帮助购房 / 购车人做更好的财务决策</p>
    <div class="editorial-grid">
      <a href="#" class="article-card reveal" aria-label="文章：澳洲 refinance 完全指南">
        <div class="article-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(156,74,46,.1), rgba(52,73,94,.15));" aria-hidden="true">
          🔄
        </div>
